Log Explorer is now GA Cloudflare Log Explorer is now generally available! =
We've heard your feedback and worked hard to bring powerful observability a=
nd forensics capabilities directly into your Cloudflare dashboard. Get Log =
Explorer Logs are stored on Cloudflare's global network using the R2 object=
 storage platform. Log Explorer gives you a comprehensive view of your Clou=
dflare logs, helping you: Quickly detect, triage, and investigate security =
incidents and application performance issues, leading to faster recovery ti=
mes. Easily monitor security and performance using intuitive custom dashboa=
rds, even creating charts with a natural language interface. Perform in-dep=
th investigations and save queries for collaboration with your team. Log Ex=
plorer is designed to streamline your operations by offering direct mitigat=
ion capabilities within your Cloudflare customer dashboard. Log Explorer is=
 built on Cloudflare R2 using Apache Parquet and Delta Lake to ensure effic=
ient data storage and querying. Log Explorer billing is based on the number=
 of GBs indexed and stored, at $1 per GB (first 10GB are completely free!).=
